{"tid":798292,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"朗拿度即將購入西甲球會華拉度列","createTime":"2018-08-29T07:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T09:37:43.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d6d38da7f5e5556291f8f5e8a40395f38da37365","tid":798292,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T07:53:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">世上只有一個球王朗拿度,賤種粉縮埋你老母個西度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=efwaYty1auiAWLC5f5q%2FEtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=5b9c20ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】西班牙《馬卡報》披露，今年41歲的巴西傳奇朗拿度（Ronaldo），將斥資3000萬歐元，購入在今季相隔4年後重返西甲的升班馬華拉度列。 據知，收購的談判正在進行中，大哨有望成為新主席，取代在位多年的卡路士蘇亞雷斯。墨西哥富豪Ernesto Tinajero年前亦曾希望收購華拉度列，但最終失敗。 前巴西國腳大哨曾效國際米蘭、巴塞隆拿、皇家馬德里等勁旅，3度榮膺世界足球先生，率領巴西贏過2次世界盃，一度成為世界盃史上入球王，2011年2月14日正式掛靴。 大哨退役後似乎愛上做老闆，曾擁有美國低組別球隊勞德代爾堡前鋒，直至2016年解散。"},{"pid":"a19820e219d1dc8096cd3daf4a1161a5fe8c5b07","tid":798292,"uid":2676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:03:15.000Z","msg":"之前又話有病？"},{"pid":"3874cf599a226f24863313e8e5f33eec738d515c","tid":798292,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a19820e219d1dc8096cd3daf4a1161a5fe8c5b07","tid":798292,"uid":2676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:03:15.000Z","msg":"之前又話有病？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"賤種朗就有病"},{"pid":"ead38ec1ebc306faf9c4373ece38d35d9d27137d","tid":798292,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:16:47.000Z","msg":"仲咁有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d29403533746e7049e717bb18d3dd4a116de9e4","tid":798292,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:19:56.000Z","msg":"前巴西國腳大哨曾效國際米蘭、巴塞隆拿、皇家馬德里等勁旅<br />\n<br />\n無乞衣米蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s